  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Thread the pork, onion, and bell pepper onto skewers.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together mirin, pickle juice, olive oil, garlic, paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Brush the mixture onto the skewers.",
    "Grill the skewers for 10-12 minutes, turning occasionally.",
    "Let the skewers rest for 5 minutes before serving.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy.",
    "Garnish with fresh parsley or thyme, if desired."
